Pastors and Preachers Condemns Violent Crackdown on Peaceful Protesters<br />
<br />
Dozens of pastors and preachers hold a press conference as they recount what they had experienced from June 11 to June 12, strongly condemning the violent crackdown by the Hong Kong Police force on peaceful protesters. A few of the pastors sobbed as they tell their stories，one of them claimed that when he requested the police officers to give warnings before pushing or dispersing the protesters; only to get a provocative response, &quot;Call upon your Jesus to show himself before me!&quot;

